<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 02-12-13 - RFI Filter Kit For Rear Mounted CEC Modules</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi021213" tsitype="engine">
        <tsinumber>02-12-13</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>April 2003</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>Engine</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>RFI Filter Kit For Rear Mounted CEC Modules</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <engfamgroup/>

                <engfam>DT 466
                    <snrange>1038626 and above</snrange>
                </engfam>
                <engfam>DT 530
                    <snrange>1038626 and above</snrange>
                </engfam>
                <engfam>HT 530
                    <snrange>1038626 and above</snrange>
                </engfam>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>A new RFI (Radio Frequency Interference) filter kit is released for service. Reason for the new
                    kit is to suppress the RFI noise that interferes with 2-way radio operations on engines, serial
                    number 1038626 and above, with rear mount CEC modules.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Some severe cases may require replacement of the engine harness with a new shielded
                            harness, part number 1833443C95. This new shielded harness was implemented on all production
                            engines 4/7/03 beginning with engine serial number 1405311, and is now available for
                            service.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <para>A similar kit exists for engines with front mount CEC modules.</para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
        <partsinfo>
            <table id="t0212131">
                <title>RFI Filter Kit Part Numbers For Both Front And Rear Mount CEC Modules</title>
                <tgroup cols="2">
                    <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.01*"/>
                    <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="0.99*"/>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Front mount CEC modules</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Rear mount CEC modules</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1833128C1</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>1842158C92</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
            <para>The RFI filter kit, 1842158C92, contains the following parts.</para>
            <figure id="f0212131" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../tsifigures/A0903.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="232px"
                         scalefitheight="232px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 1. RFI filter kit</caption>
            </figure>
            <seqlist style="arabic">
                <item>
                    <para>1000 pF capacitance RFI filter with 3/8 inch ring terminals 127 mm (5 inches in length from
                        middle of ring terminals)
                    </para>
                    <seqlist>
                        <item>
                            <para>Non capacitor end</para>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <para>Capacitor</para>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <para>Capacitor end</para>
                        </item>
                    </seqlist>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Star washer</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>M10 x 20 mm bolt</para>
                </item>
            </seqlist>
            <para>Also included in the RFI filter kit is the instruction sheet 1171796R1.</para>
        </partsinfo>
    </tsi>
</isis>
